targets.rawQuery: SELECT     test,     metric.1 AS name,     metric.2 AS value,     metric.3 AS units FROM (     SELECT         test,         arrayJoin(metric) AS metric     FROM     (         SELECT             test,             arrayZip(name, value, units) AS metric         FROM         (             SELECT                 anyIf(test_name, test_name != '') AS test,                 groupArray(metric_name) AS name,                 groupArray(metric_value) AS value,                 groupArray(metric_units) AS units             FROM messages             WHERE test_id LIKE '/aaefb378-a1e2-11ea-99c9-2477034de0ec/1%' AND message_keyword IN ('TEST', 'METRIC')             GROUP BY test_key         )     ) ) WHERE name != ''

targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.query:
SELECT
    test,
    metric.1 AS name,
    metric.2 AS value,
    metric.3 AS units
FROM
(
    SELECT
        test,
        arrayJoin(metric) AS metric
    FROM
    (
        SELECT
            test,
            arrayZip(name, value, units) AS metric
        FROM
        (
            SELECT
                anyIf(test_name, test_name != '') AS test,
                groupArray(metric_name) AS name,
                groupArray(metric_value) AS value,
                groupArray(metric_units) AS units
            FROM messages
            WHERE test_id LIKE '$test_id%' AND message_keyword IN ('TEST', 'METRIC')
            GROUP BY test_key
        )
    )
)
WHERE name != ''

targets.query:
SELECT
    test,
    requirement.1 AS name,
    requirement.2 AS Version,
    requirement.3 AS Description,
    requirement.4 AS Link
FROM
(
    SELECT
        test,
        arrayJoin(requirement) AS requirement
    FROM
    (
        SELECT
            test,
            arrayZip(name, version, description, link) AS requirement
        FROM
        (
            SELECT
                anyIf(test_name, test_name != '') AS test,
                groupArray(requirement_name) AS name,
                groupArray(requirement_version) AS version,
                groupArray(requirement_description) AS description,
                groupArray(requirement_link) AS link
            FROM messages
            WHERE test_id LIKE '$test_id%' AND message_keyword IN ('TEST', 'REQUIREMENT')
            GROUP BY test_key
        )
    )
)
WHERE name != ''

targets.query:
SELECT
    test,
    ticket.1 AS name,
    ticket.2 AS link
FROM
(
    SELECT
        test,
        arrayJoin(ticket) AS ticket
    FROM
    (
        SELECT
            test,
            arrayZip(name, link) AS ticket
        FROM
        (
            SELECT
                anyIf(test_name, test_name != '') AS test,
                groupArray(ticket_name) AS name,
                groupArray(ticket_link) AS link
            FROM messages
            WHERE test_id LIKE '$test_id%' AND message_keyword IN ('TEST', 'TICKET')
            GROUP BY test_key
        )
    )
)
WHERE name != ''

targets.query:
SELECT
    anyIf(test_name, test_name != '') AS name,
    toUInt8(anyIf(result_type, result_type != '')) AS result,
    max(message_rtime) AS duration,
    max(message_time) AS time,
    test_id
FROM messages
WHERE test_parent = '$test_id' AND message_keyword IN ('TEST', 'RESULT') AND if('$show_steps' != 'True' , test_type >= 20, 1) 
GROUP BY test_id
ORDER BY time, test_id DESC

targets.query:
SELECT
    toString(message_keyword) AS _keyword,
    concat(upper(substr(_keyword,1,1)), lower(substr(_keyword,2,length(_keyword)-1))) AS Keyword,
    concat(repeat('      ', message_level), multiIf(
      message_keyword = 'PROTOCOL', protocol_version,
      message_keyword = 'VERSION', framework_version,
      message_keyword = 'TEST', test_name,
      message_keyword = 'RESULT', toString(result_type),
      message_keyword = 'ATTRIBUTE', concat(attribute_name, ', value: ', attribute_value),
      message_keyword = 'TAG', tag_value,
      message_keyword = 'ARGUMENT', concat(argument_name, ', value: ', argument_value),
      message_keyword = 'REQUIREMENT', concat(requirement_name, ', version: ', requirement_version),
      message_keyword = 'METRIC', concat(metric_name, ', value: ', toString(metric_value), ', units: ', metric_units),
      message_keyword = 'TICKET', ticket_name,
      message_keyword = 'VALUE', concat(value_name, ', value: ', value_value),
      message_keyword in ('NONE', 'NOTE', 'DEBUG', 'EXCEPTION', 'INPUT','TRACE'), message,
      message_keyword = 'EXAMPLE', concat(toString(example_row), ', columns: ',toString(example_columns), ', values: ', toString(example_values)),
      message_keyword in ('NODE', 'MAP'), concat(node_name, ', module: ', node_module, ', next: ', toString(node_nexts), ', in: ', toString(node_ins), ', out: ', toString(node_outs)),
      ''
    )) AS Message,
    message_rtime AS rtime,
    toDateTime64(message_time,3) AS Time
FROM $table
WHERE test_id LIKE '$test_id%'
ORDER BY message_time, message_num
